Subject: drm/amd/display: drop dc_validate_guaranteed
Git-commit: 6133470c8e2ffdc6a5d67a1d79a9a0c1c0a94a10
Patch-mainline: v4.18-rc1
References: FATE#326289 FATE#326079 FATE#326049 FATE#322398 FATE#326166

